OL,3,CMan jailed for sending threatening
OL,4,Cemails to politician Caroline Nokes
OL,6,FA 33-year-old man has been jailed for
OL,7,Fseven months after sending threatening
OL,8,Femails to a female politician.
OL,10,FLiam McCarthy, of Copperfield Road,
OL,11,FSouthampton, "continuously" sent
OL,12,Femails and left voicemails for
OL,13,FConservative politician Caroline Nokes
OL,14,Fbetween May 15 2022 and March 4 2023.
OL,16,FMs Nokes was the MP for Romsey and
OL,17,FSouthampton North at the time of the
OL,18,Foffending, and is currently standing
OL,19,Ffor re-election.
