OL,6,FMcCarthy also left threatening
OL,7,Fvoicemails for Steve Smith, former
OL,8,Fhead of stronger communities,
OL,9,Fneighbourhoods and housing, at
OL,10,FSouthampton City Council between
OL,11,FNovember 14 and 21 2022.
OL,13,FHe was jailed for seven months at
OL,14,FSouthampton Magistrates' Court on
OL,15,FWednesday, the CPS said.
