OL,3,CMan jailed for sending threatening
OL,4,Cemails to politician Caroline Nokes
OL,6,FVictoria Hill, prosecuting, told
OL,7,FSouthampton Magistrates' Court in a
OL,8,Fprevious hearing that the defendant
OL,9,Ffirst contacted Ms Nokes to raise a
OL,10,F"lack of support for people aged
OL,11,Fbetween 18 and 25".
OL,13,FMs Hill said: "He moved on to talk
OL,14,Fabout issues he was having with the
OL,15,FDepartment of Work and Pensions and a
OL,16,Fdebt collection agency.
OL,18,F"They didn't end up seeing one another
OL,19,Fbecause the defendant cancelled his
OL,20,Fappointment because he felt
OL,21,Funprepared."
