OL,4,Cemails to politician Caroline Nokes
OL,6,FThe court heard how the emails
OL,7,Fcontinued and in August 2022 they
OL,8,Fstarted to become threatening.
OL,10,FPreviously describing the voicemails
OL,11,Fto the court, Ms Hill said: "They were
OL,12,Fmore overtly threatening. He said
OL,13,Fthings like, 'I will find you, I will
OL,14,Ff****** destroy you, I swear to god, I
OL,15,Fmean that as a threat."
